---
import { SITE } from '../../config/site';

const domain = new URL(SITE.url).hostname;
---

<section class="pt-12 pb-20 px-6" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:ou088s">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:frzriq">
    <h1 style="color: var(--text);" class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:518mfk">Terms Of Service</h1>
    <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="text-sm mb-8" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:58sd35">Last Updated on [10/12/2025]</p>

    <div class="max-w-none" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:frzrir">
      <section class="mb-12" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:ou088t">
        <h2 style="color: var(--text);" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:5ia9kh">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:58sd34">
          By accessing or using this website (https://asianfoodsdaily.com/), you agree to comply with these Terms and Conditions. If you disagree, do not use the site.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:ou088u">
        <h2 style="color: var(--text);" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:5ia9ki">2. User Responsibilities</h2>
        <ul style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:rxn825">Do not use the site for unlawful purposes or to harass others.</li>
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:rxn826">Avoid posting harmful, defamatory, or spam content in comments or interactive areas.</li>
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:rxn82s">You are responsible for verifying recipe accuracy, dietary suitability, and allergen information before use.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:ou088q">
        <h2 style="color: var(--text);" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:5ia9kg">3. Disclaimers</h2>
        <ul style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:rxn82t">Recipes, nutritional information, and cooking results may vary. Use at your own risk.</li>
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:rxn82u">The site does not guarantee uninterrupted, error-free access.</li>
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:rxn82v">Links to third-party sites (e.g., ingredient suppliers, ads) are not endorsements. Review their policies separately.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:ou088r">
        <h2 style="color: var(--text);" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:5ia9kh">4. Affiliate and Sponsorship Disclosures</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:58sd33">
          The site may use affiliate links (e.g., Amazon Associates) or sponsored content. Purchases via these links may earn us a commission at no extra cost to you.
        </p>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:58sd32">
          Opinions in sponsored posts are always our own.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:ou088s">
        <h2 style="color: var(--text);" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:5ia9ki">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:58sd31">
          Asianfoodsdaily and its owner is not liable for:
        </p>
        <ul style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:rxn82w">Damages from using recipes, advice, or external links.</li>
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:rxn82x">Technical issues (e.g., site downtime, data loss).</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:ou088t">
        <h2 style="color: var(--text);" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:5ia9kj">6. Termination</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:58sd30">
          We reserve the right to block users or remove content violating these terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:ou088u">
        <h2 style="color: var(--text);" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:som4kl">7. Governing Law</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:58sd2z">
          Subject to the laws of [ Texas/USA,], excluding conflict of law principles.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:ou088v">
        <h2 style="color: var(--text);" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:som4km">8. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:58sd2y">
          We may update these terms. Continued use after changes implies acceptance. Check this page periodically.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:ou088v">
        <h2 style="color: var(--text);" class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:5ia9kj">9. Contact</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="mb-4" data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:58sd32">
          Questions? Reach us at:
        </p>
        <ul style="color: var(--text-muted);" class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:rxn821">By email: hello@asianfoodsdaily.com</li>
          <li data-ps="src/components/legal/TermsContent.astro:rxn822">By visiting this page on our website: {SITE.url}/contact</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
